		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="437" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之风脱去外壳暴露核心，在周围产生真空场牵引玩家，持续造成<span color="#7fffd7">25%</span><span>伤害，之后产生剧烈爆炸，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">150%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="428" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之风蜕去外壳，将风立方从空中坠下，每个造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害，共计下落5个风立方，风立方落地产生</span><span textDecoration="underline">风棱晶</span><span>，打碎风棱晶才会产生风场。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="671" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之风盘旋升空，于空中向地面注入风元素气旋，持续造成<span color="#7fffd7">25%</span><span>伤害，同时场地出现8个游离的龙卷风，龙卷风可被</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">冰</span><span>染色，接触造成</span><span color="#ffeebf">对应元素</span><span>的</span><span color="#ffeebf">75%</span><span>伤害，最终形成对应</span><span textDecoration="underline">元素之微粒</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="425" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之风在地面高速旋转，在其周围持续造成<span color="#7fffd7">10%</span><span>伤害，吸收风之微粒产生大范围冲击波，造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，吸收3个微粒后停止攻击，暴露核心；若吸收其他元素则会爆炸，并立即停止攻击暴露核心。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_14.png')" x="720" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
