		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_20.png')" x="596" y="171" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_21.png')" x="576" y="150" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之风开阵，8个风立方外壳围一圈暴露核心，发射3个风弹，每个风弹造成<span color="#7fffd7">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="432" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">生命值低于5%时，无相之风召唤5个<span textDecoration="underline">复苏风晶球</span><span>，其中一个风晶球是游离的；周围产生4个风场，复苏持续15s，每个风之晶球恢复无相之风</span><span color="#7fffd7">12.5%</span><span>生命值，无晶球时恢复</span><span color="#72ffdc">5%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1008" width="289" height="58" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">元素之微粒：触碰产生6个对应元素微粒。<br/>复苏风晶球：触碰产生3个<span color="#7fffd7">风元素微粒</span><span>。<br/>风棱晶：3次次数盾，击破产生风场。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_22.png')" x="1268" y="171" blendMode="normal">
