		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_28.png')" x="1268" y="395" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_29.png')" x="1248" y="374" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_30.png')" x="596" y="395" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_31.png')" x="576" y="374" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="435" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之风升空化成风晶蝶，不断抖动周围空气，持续大范围造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，使用下落攻击命中以打断其技能。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_32.png')" x="719" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/无相之风%B7间奏曲%B7暴风之蝶.assets/Image_33.png')" x="1391" y="362">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="428" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之风将外壳化为成两面墙，随后夹击，造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。夹击时产生3道风刃，每个风刃造成</span><span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
